s390/cpuinfo: show facilities as reported by stfle

Add a new line to /proc/cpuinfo which shows all available facilities
as reported by the stfle instruction:

> cat /proc/cpuinfo
...
facilities      : 0 1 2 3 4 6 7 ...
...

